2005-05-04 16:46:41 GMT	Tobias Toedter <t.toedter@gmx.net>	patch-6

    Summary:
      Removed suffix flag "l"
    Revision:
      medicalterms--main--1.0--patch-6

    This flag was newly created by me for words ending on -logie
    and got expanded to "-logie, -loge, -logen, -login, -loginnen".
    As this is not supported by Bjoern Jacke's original dictionary,
    I dropped the flag and used the suffixes /FN on "-loge" instead.

    modified files:
     dicts/medizin.txt


